freeflow Data Structures

Here are the data structures with brief descriptions:
surfit::flow_garbageStruct for deletion of pointers
surfit::freeflow_managerServes file_load, file_save, clear_data and mem_info commands for libfreeflow
surfit::lcm_simpleLaw of conservation of mass for homogeneous formation (constants for formation permeability, thick and liquid viscosity) and stationary filtration
surfit::lcm_simple_userInterface class for making equations from lcm_simple_user
surfit::pareaArea with a constant "production" value
surfit::parea_garbageStruct for deletion of pointers
surfit::parea_userClass for data usage in solving algorithm
surfit::pcntrLine with "production" values
surfit::pcntr_garbageStruct for deletion of pointers
surfit::pcntr_userClass for data usage in solving algorithm
surfit::pisoLine with a constant value (pisoline)
surfit::piso_garbageStruct for deletion of pointers
surfit::piso_userClass for data usage in solving algorithm
surfit::ptaskScattered "production" data points for func calculation
surfit::ptask_garbageStruct for deletion of pointers
surfit::ptask_userClass for ptask usage in solving algorithm
